title: 1989 Angst unter den Sternen (Fear under the stars)

sources.title: 1989 Angst unter den Sternen (Fear under the stars)
sources.description: With Angelika and Michael Cording (text and acting), Flash Gilden (musik and acting), Rolo Schriefer (fotos) and Fred Keil The defeat of the squatters at Marienstrasse in Cologne - Ehrenfeld is for Michael and Angelika Cording a cry-out about their own failures and the failures of the others.
